IThcWidget:
  - common abstract interface to all widget
  - set_mode/get_mode/get_supported_mode
  - set_param/get_param
  - set_skin/get_skin
  - signal_mode_change()/signal_skin_change()
  
ThcWidget:
  - implementation of IThcWidget (all widget should derive from ThcWidget, not IThcWidget)
  - a widget must contains Param::Ref variables members for each parameter: Param::Ref m_memberparam;
  - each widget should register its parameters: set_param("param_name", m_memberparam);
  
Param
  - type: Param::Ref
  - create one with Param::Ref skin = Param::create_skin();
  - a param is a value controled by a widget

Skin: 
  - type: Skin::Ref
  - create one with Skin::Ref skin = Skin::create_skin();
  - a skin is a xmlnode and a set of images defining the skin of one widget
  
ModeManager: 
  - singleton that toggle the mode(connect/normal) of groups of widgets

SkinManager:
  - singleton that contain all Skin instance (all xml + images need to skin widget)







=============

CloWidget::Slider : a simple slider
